.Dd Nov 12, 2025
.Dt gufi_stat
.Os Linux
.Sh NAME
.Nm gufi_stat
.Nd display file status
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op options
FILE [FILE ...]
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Display file status.

.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width -indent
.It Fl -help
help
.It Fl v, -version
show program's version number and exit
.It Fl c, -format FORMAT
use the specified FORMAT instead of the default; output a newline after each use of FORMAT
.It Fl t, -terse
print the information in terse form
.It Fl V, -verbose
Show the actual command being run

.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Bl -tag -width -indent
.It EXIT_SUCCESS or EXIT_FAILURE
.El

.Pp
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width -compact
.It gufi_stat
.It @INSTALL_CONFIG@
.El

\# .Sh BUGS
\# .Sh EXAMPLE
